diff --git a/gamemodes/README.md b/gamemodes/README.md
--- a/gamemodes/README.md
+++ b/gamemodes/README.md
@@ -1,3 +1,17 @@
+# LS:RP Message Style
+
+Quy uoc message chung:
+
+- Trang `#FFFFFF`: heading va noi dung can nhan manh.
+- Xam nhat `#BFC0C2`: noi dung he thong chinh.
+- Xam dam `#858585`: separator va thong tin phu.
+- Xanh navy `#264A73`: ten, ID, tien, command, vehicle va cac gia tri quan trong.
+- Do burgundy `#7A2929`: loi, canh bao va trang thai bat thuong.
+
+Message gameplay nen theo cau truc:
+`Hanh dong + doi tuong + ket qua + huong dan tiep theo (neu can)`.
+
+Khong tao README rieng trong tung module. Moi ghi chu gamemode duoc cap nhat tai file nay.
+
